Security Tools
----------------

AdminPulse (DoiT)
https://github.com/doitintl/DoiT-AdminPulse-for-Workspace
https://adminpulse.doit.com/ (has embedded video demonstrating tool use)

GAM
https://github.com/GAM-team/GAM
"GAM is a command line tool for Google Workspace admins to manage domain and user settings quickly and easily."

GAT+
https://gatlabs.com/products/gat/
https://workspace.google.com/marketplace/app/gat+/199329000796
(provides a more intuitive and comprehensive dashboard for GWS focused on auditing; costly, but includes initial free trial)

